ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: An informative and entertaining weekly clinical research variety show
I would recommend it to any psychology student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Talks were both informative in the content in great examples of what to do during a professional talk
A number of the speakers who visited this fall conduct research in my subfield, and having the opportunity to hear them speak was invaluable!
It has introduced me to interesting research being performed and allowed me to talk with researchers.
Seeing presentations of exciting current work in my field was invaluable for informing my research and inspiring new ideas.
This course deepened my understanding of some current related work in the field.
